data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bath home built in 2022 by GHO Homes boasting 10ft ceilings throughout and no HOA restrictions. Step into the gourmet kitchen, with double ovens, quartz countertops, backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and recessed lighting which create an ambiance of culinary delight. Relax in the screened porch overlooking the potential pool area. Inside, enjoy trey ceilings, a laundry room, and a master suite with dual sinks and two walk-in closets, with impact windows and doors. With no HOA, personalize your outdoor space to your liking. Don't miss out--schedule a viewing today!
